 United States. Available from: URL: https://www.cdc.gov/vaccines/covid-19/info-by-product/clinical-considerations.html." ([2021, Jan 6]):[2] US Food and Drug Administration "Emergency Use Authorization. Emergency Use Authorization (EUA) information, and list of all current EUAs. Available from: URL: https://www.fda.gov/emergency-preparedness-and-response/mcm-legal-regulatory-and-policy-framework/emergency-use-authorization." ([2020 Apr 06]):', 1767363023);
